description_en: Immediately upon entering you are presented with breathtaking panoramic views. The gracious living room and dining room are fronted with 10' floor-to-ceiling windows offering tremendous light and incredible views of Central Park, Adobe Circle, the Hudson River, George Washington Bridge, Statue of Liberty and beyond. Enjoy the most incredible sunrises and sunsets from this 73rd floor. Residents are treated to incomparable luxury living and enjoy five-star amenities such as: White gloved, 24-hour concierge, valet and doorman, Private elevators, Forty-thousand square foot fitness facility and 75-foot enclosed swimming pool,The Mandarin Spa, Hardwood floors and high ceilings, Granite countertops with Miele appliances, Marble-accented windowed baths, Smart technology with customized sound and lighting.
